race.comment: SUMO SANDY (3) can notch up a hat-trick. He's won both starts this time in, backing up the dominant Kerang maiden win with a strong victory at Pakenham over this trip second up. He's drawn wide again here but Meech should send him straight to the front again and take catching again. ITSUKUSHIMA (2) continues to race well but just find one better, looking to have the race won at Moe last time before getting nabbed on the line. He'll give a sight again. STORM AHEAD (7) is going well. He won well over this route two back and can be in this for a long way. PHINEAS (9) next best off a handy maiden win here last start.
